title: Wassily Kandinsky 2024 Mini Wall Calendar
description:
One of the most monumental and prolific artists of the 20th century, Kandinsky's work is found in major museums worldwide. Although his art spanned many periods and styles, he is perhaps most recognized for his bold use of color, shape and line in his geometric compositions. Kandinsky is credited with being the first purely abstract artist. Many of his most powerful paintings are reproduced in this dramatic and beautiful calendar.

  • Dimensions: 7 x 7 in.
  • Includes major international holidays, lunar phases, and zodiac signs
  • Features 7 languages: Italian, English, German, French, Spanish, Portuguese, Japanese
